      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_18_2443-2498",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2443-2498",
      "markText": "后来，我也慢慢地学会了做这些事情，把门外的阶坎扫干净，给路过歇脚的人递水，不用母亲吩咐，我只要看到了就会去做。",
      "totalCount": 1566,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2443&rangeEnd=2498",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2443&rangeEnd=2498"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_15_799-882",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "799-882",
      "markText": "不捡起来的意思是把孩子直接放进装满水的桶里，待孩子没气了就在后山上挖个小坑埋掉。孩子还没开始养，感情还没建立起来，大概那时候吃不饱穿不暖的父母这样选择也可以忍下心来。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=799&rangeEnd=882",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=799&rangeEnd=882"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_17_3397-3485",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3397-3485",
      "markText": "每次分完粮食我都要试图从母亲的背篓里多抢一点来背，母亲每次也都会象征性地给我背篓里多加两把粮食或者多加几个土豆几个红薯，那种卑微的慈爱和依赖，一直是我记忆深处最温暖踏实的东西。",
      "totalCount": 738,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3397&rangeEnd=3485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3397&rangeEnd=3485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_18_2763-2799",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2763-2799",
      "markText": "可是母亲仍然愿意关心那些比她更穷的人，而且总是小心翼翼地护着他们的体面。",
      "totalCount": 735,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2763&rangeEnd=2799",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2763&rangeEnd=2799"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_15_4375-4412",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "4375-4412",
      "markText": "小时候父亲在我心中又是一个好得不得了的样子，因为那就是母亲口中父亲的样子。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4375&rangeEnd=4412",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4375&rangeEnd=4412"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_20_2573-2611",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2573-2611",
      "markText": "母亲说的最后一句话，我俯在她嘴边才听清楚的最后一句话——“甲儿，带妈回家”。",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2573&rangeEnd=2611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2573&rangeEnd=2611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_16_3535-3601",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3535-3601",
      "markText": "在我记忆中，母亲跟我说我是她的贵人，多数时间就是在小时候。慢慢地，我也开始相信，我就是那个通过算命先生的口让母亲留在了人世间的贵人。",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3535&rangeEnd=3601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3535&rangeEnd=3601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_16_1654-1747",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1654-1747",
      "markText": "她首先拿出毛主席语录读了几句“一个人犯了错误不要紧，改了就是好同志。要允许犯错误、允许改正错误”，然后说来开会之前已经把苗子都拔掉喂猪了，接着就喊：“毛主席万岁！”居然把生产队长噎住了，",
      "totalCount": 637,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1654&rangeEnd=1747",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1654&rangeEnd=1747"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_18_947-1006",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "947-1006",
      "markText": "还记得当时母亲拉下脸呵斥我：人不到活不下去的地步，怎么会借盐吃？我们不借给他们，他们就没地方借了，以后不准你说这种话！",
      "totalCount": 620,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=947&rangeEnd=1006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=947&rangeEnd=1006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_18_3112-3179",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "3112-3179",
      "markText": "母亲的悲悯心似乎与生俱来，我长大后去到一些名山大川，看到寺庙里供着的菩萨的样子，总会想到母亲的模样。特别是母亲去世以后，我更是这样想。",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3112&rangeEnd=3179",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3112&rangeEnd=3179"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_19_1845-1915",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1845-1915",
      "markText": "不等大人都上桌，孩子都不会动筷子；有好点的菜会互相夹一点；如果孩子先吃完，放下筷子前会双手端筷跟父母说一声“爸爸妈妈我吃完了，你们慢点吃”。",
      "totalCount": 572,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1845&rangeEnd=1915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1845&rangeEnd=1915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_16_2857-2889",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2857-2889",
      "markText": "40多年过去了，母亲当时满脸的汗水红扑扑的笑容仍然令我记忆犹新。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2857&rangeEnd=2889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2857&rangeEnd=2889"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_18_2029-2090",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2029-2090",
      "markText": "于是母亲让我进灶屋给他们父子拿筷子，又端出一个装酱的土碗，端了一缸子水放在他们父子旁边，叮嘱我拿着煤油灯在旁边给他们照亮。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2029&rangeEnd=2090",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2029&rangeEnd=2090"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_15_2609-2641",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2609-2641",
      "markText": "母亲只有一米五几的身高，体重八十几斤，但是她背得起上百斤的东西。",
      "totalCount": 495,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2609&rangeEnd=2641",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2609&rangeEnd=2641"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_16_3100-3152",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3100-3152",
      "markText": "那几乎是我记事后唯一一次要母亲背，我就那样趴在母亲的背上，母亲身上的汗味是香的，和着一点青草香气的感觉。",
      "totalCount": 495,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3100&rangeEnd=3152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3100&rangeEnd=3152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_19_665-686",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "665-686",
      "markText": "母亲经常挂在嘴边的一句话是“爱干净穷不久”",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=665&rangeEnd=686",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=665&rangeEnd=686"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_15_3505-3541",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "3505-3541",
      "markText": "凌晨的时候我落地了。当时母亲的身边只有一个人，就是我1岁零5个月的姐姐。",
      "totalCount": 430,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3505&rangeEnd=3541",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3505&rangeEnd=3541"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300136012_20_2841-2900",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2841-2900",
      "markText": "换好衣服后我发现母亲的头发根里好像还有一点汗津津的样子，就说还要给母亲最后再洗一次头发，爱人和姐姐哭着抱住我阻止了我。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2841&rangeEnd=2900",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2841&rangeEnd=2900"
    },
    {
