      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2100-2151",
      "markText": "每年春节吃团年饭的时候，吃饭前母亲总会要我们每一个人说一下过去一年最高兴的事，然后说一句对来年的吉祥话",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300136012&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2100&rangeEnd=2151",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/de132b00813ab9ba1g0124df?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2100&rangeEnd=2151"
